|1 |└─EXCHANGE OUT REMOTE                      |       |
|2 |  └─TOP-N SORT                             |       |
|3 |    └─HASH GROUP BY                        |       |
|4 |      └─NESTED-LOOP JOIN                   |       |
|5 |        ├─SUBPLAN SCAN                     |avg    |
|6 |        │ └─SCALAR GROUP BY                |       |
|7 |        │   └─TABLE FULL SCAN              |scores |
|8 |        └─NESTED-LOOP JOIN                 |       |
