|10|          │ ├─TABLE FULL SCAN              |majors |
|11|          │ └─SORT                         |       |
|12|          │   └─MERGE RIGHT OUTER JOIN     |       |
|13|          │     ├─TABLE FULL SCAN          |classes|
|14|          │     └─SORT                     |       |
|15|          │       └─MERGE JOIN             |       |
|16|          │         ├─SORT                 |       |
|17|          │         │ └─SUBPLAN SCAN       |nc     |
|18|          │         │   └─HASH GROUP BY    |       |
|19|          │         │     └─TABLE FULL SCAN|scores |
|20|          │         └─TABLE FULL SCAN      |s      |
|21|          └─SUBPLAN SCAN                   |sc     |
|22|            └─TOP-N SORT                   |       |
|23|              └─TABLE FULL SCAN            |scores |
